<i> are criminally prosecuted,</i>

00:02:50.336 --> 00:02:52.271
<i> which means
 the parents go to jail</i>

00:02:52.304 --> 00:02:53.940
<i> while their kids
 are given a blanket</i>

00:02:53.973 --> 00:02:55.541
<i> and shipped off
 to a detention center</i>

00:02:55.574 --> 00:02:57.343
<i> to hang out in a cage.</i>

00:02:57.376 --> 00:02:59.312
Some have referred to them
as "cages,"

00:02:59.345 --> 00:03:01.547
but keep in mind,
they built walls

00:03:01.580 --> 00:03:03.316
out of chain-link fences.

00:03:03.349 --> 00:03:04.951
GREY:
<i> Sorry, not cages.</i>

00:03:04.984 --> 00:03:06.886
<i> I meant a wall made out
 of a chain-link fence.</i>

00:03:06.919 --> 00:03:08.287
<i> Totally different.</i>

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:10.656
<i> The point is
 it's not really that bad.</i>

00:03:10.689 --> 00:03:13.426
It was a shocking sight
to walk in initially,

00:03:13.459 --> 00:03:16.362
just to see so many people
so distressed,

00:03:16.395 --> 00:03:18.564
a number of people crying.

00:03:18.597 --> 00:03:20.333
They look like big cages

00:03:20.366 --> 00:03:22.702
or maybe the way you would
construct a dog kennel.

00:03:22.735 --> 00:03:23.869
Do you know kids?

00:03:23.902 --> 00:03:25.871
You throw a cage
in the middle of the room,

00:03:25.904 --> 00:03:27.006
and they'll run into it.

00:03:27.039 --> 00:03:29.609
It's, like, basically
a free jungle gym.

00:03:29.642 --> 00:03:31.811
Well, it didn't appear
that any children

00:03:31.844 --> 00:03:34.146
were having much fun
when I was there.

00:03:34.179 --> 00:03:37.750
GREY:<i> Merkley seems determined
 to inhumanely force Trump</i>

00:03:37.783 --> 00:03:40.987
<i> to separate from his campaign
 promises on immigration.</i>

00:03:41.020 --> 00:03:43.589
I would love to be able
to rip that policy from them

00:03:43.622 --> 00:03:44.957
and-and end it.

00:03:44.990 --> 00:03:46.859
You're a monster.

00:03:46.892 --> 00:03:48.361
<i> Merkley's ridiculous stunt</i>

00:03:48.394 --> 00:03:49.862
<i> of showing the plight
 of children</i>

00:03:49.895 --> 00:03:51.897
<i> in cages on American soil</i>

00:03:51.930 --> 00:03:53.366
<i> is somehow working.</i>

00:03:53.399 --> 00:03:56.235
<i> Democrats, former first ladies,
 current first ladies,</i>

00:03:56.268 --> 00:03:57.603
